1
00:00:06,120 --> 00:00:07,400
Hello, everyone.

2
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:09,000
I'm reporting from Junlin Group.

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:10,400
According to insiders,

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,280
Shen Tingyuan, Chairman of Junlin Group,

5
00:00:12,280 --> 00:00:15,280
recently suffered a sudden stroke
due to emotional agitation

6
00:00:15,280 --> 00:00:17,120
while handling
internal company decisions.

7
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:19,080
He was rushed to
the hospital for emergency treatment,

8
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:21,200
and his condition
is still under observation.

9
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:22,600
Prior to this,

10
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:25,320
the largest shareholder, Shen Gu,

11
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:26,560
will call a general meeting

12
00:00:26,720 --> 00:00:28,320
to elect a new
chairman for Junlin Group.

13
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:34,600
Are you feeling hot?

14
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:36,800
You're sweating quite a bit.

15
00:00:37,680 --> 00:00:38,800
Are you in pain?

16
00:00:50,420 --> 00:00:51,440
Shen Hao,

17
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:55,240
I understand how you feel right now.

18
00:00:57,040 --> 00:00:58,360
Your dad will get better.

19
00:01:04,880 --> 00:01:06,400
What's the point of getting better?

20
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:09,040
Waking up just to face his own failure?

21
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:11,320
He'd be better off dead.

22
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:12,800
Hao.

23
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:16,240
Stop lying to me.

24
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:21,040
What a pitiful face,
so good at pretending.

25
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:24,040
You fooled me for eight whole years.

26
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:25,200
Eight years!

27
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,400
So, Wanxin, please

28
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:31,280
stop acting,

29
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,720
okay?

30
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:34,000
Hao,

31
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,880
calm down.

32
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,520
Before anything irreversible happens,

33
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,600
there's still room to fix this.

34
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:42,440
What do you mean by nothing happened?

35
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:44,800
If it weren't for Shen Gu,

36
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:47,200
I would be the one marrying you.

37
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,200
Me!

38
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,240
It's all because of Shen Gu.

39
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,760
All my misfortunes are because of him.

40
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,200
I'm telling you,

41
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,960
as long as Shen Gu dies...

42
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:57,040
Shen Hao!

43
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:58,960
This has nothing to do with Shen Gu.

44
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,200
Even without him,

45
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,800
I would never have married you.

46
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,600
Even if I have to
declare Minghui bankrupt,

47
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:05,000
I will cut ties with you.

48
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:06,200
I'm right here.

49
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:08,000
If you have the guts, come at me.

50
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:14,280
You're still defending him?

51
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:18,400
I'm the one who was hurt.

52
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,840
Me!

53
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:26,080
Listen here, once Shen Gu disappears,

54
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,600
Junlin will be mine.

55
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,280
Minghui will be mine.

56
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:34,040
And you are mine. Mine!

57
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:39,020
=Echoes of Gang City=

58
00:02:39,140 --> 00:02:42,980
=Episode 26=
(Let Tragedies Never Happen Again)

59
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:56,000
There's still no news
of Miss Lin from Gang City.

60
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,200
Miss Lin

61
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:27,120
sacrificed herself.

62
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,800
Sacrificed?

63
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,720
President of the Shen City
Chamber of Commerce,

64
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:36,280
Shen Gu, has passed away.

65
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:39,240
Shen Gu is dead.

66
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,520
Grandfather.

67
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,280
Hello, Xi.

68
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,600
Mr. Changhe.

69
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,400
Grandfather.

70
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,680
Grandfather, please don't worry.

71
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,320
Wanxin will be fine.

72
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:00,920
But before Wanxin returns,

73
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:02,760
you must take care of your health.

74
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,560
The police are investigating.

75
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,360
Shen Gu has landed in Gang City,

76
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:08,760
and he's currently
on his way back to us.

77
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,720
Yes, and tell

78
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:14,680
Shen Gu to be careful.

79
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:18,080
Wanxin and Shen Gu just got together.

80
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,880
Nothing else must happen to them.

81
00:04:21,280 --> 00:04:24,200
Don't worry, Grandfather.
Everything will be okay.

82
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:39,800
Hello,

83
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,000
it's Shen Gu.

84
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:43,480
Shen Gu, I'll give you half an hour.

85
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,080
If you don't want Xu Wanxin to die,

86
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,480
get over here right now.

87
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,120
Shen Gu, don't come!

88
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,680
He's lost his mind! Call the police!

89
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:52,520
Fine. I agree.

90
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,800
But you must ensure Wanxin's safety.

91
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,160
Then, you'd better hurry.

92
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,680
After all, I've already gone mad,

93
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:58,120
and I don't have much patience.

94
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,800
Gently!

95
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,040
This is my wife.

96
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:03,840
Hello?

97
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:04,640
Hello?

98
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:05,480
Hello?

99
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:10,590
Hello?

100
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:11,280
Fang Hongsheng,

101
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,280
there's news.

102
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,880
Shen Hao kidnapped Wanxin.

103
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,560
He's out of control now.

104
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,880
He demanded to see me alone.

105
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,280
I'm notifying the police right now.

106
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:20,400
I'll have someone track
your car's location in real-time.

107
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:21,400
Okay.

108
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:22,960
Be careful.

109
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,640
Shen Hao, let her go!

110
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:07,880
Take one more step,

111
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,720
and I'll kill her.

112
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,360
Fine.

113
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,120
Fine.

114
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:13,400
I won't move.

115
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:14,880
Don't touch her.

116
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,840
Beat him!

117
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:55,880
Shen Gu!

118
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,190
Wanxin!

119
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:52,160
Shen Gu forced my hand.

120
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,000
Wanxin!

121
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,400
Wanxin.

122
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:53,600
Wanxin.

123
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,960
Are you okay, Wanxin?

124
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:20,920
Wanxin.

125
00:12:00,260 --> 00:12:02,900
(Gang City Central Hospital)

126
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:14,800
Shen Gu...

127
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:18,360
Shen Gu.

128
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:25,200
You're awake.

129
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,520
Wanxin...

130
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,680
You're finally awake.

131
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,480
You scared me to death.

132
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:34,800
You know,

133
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:38,480
if the jade pendant
hadn't blocked the knife for you,

134
00:12:38,880 --> 00:12:39,440
I would have...

135
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:40,320
It's okay.

136
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:42,160
It's all over now.

137
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,280
Don't move.
You have a stab wound on your chest.

138
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:49,960
Lie down.

139
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:52,120
Just stay still.

140
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:57,080
Wanxin,

141
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:58,960
it's all right.

142
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,280
Does it hurt?

143
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:01,160
No, it doesn't.

144
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:05,680
I was just dreaming.

145
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:08,550
I dreamed you were calling my name.

146
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,400
And then, I woke up.

147
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:12,960
Don't cry.

148
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,600
How is he? Is he out of danger?

149
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:30,840
Fine.

150
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:40,160
How is it? Is he out?

151
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:06,680
It's okay now.

152
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:08,280
It's okay now.

153
00:14:55,830 --> 00:15:01,310
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

154
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:08,390
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

155
00:15:09,430 --> 00:15:14,470
♪You turn and look back at me♪

156
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:21,110
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

157
00:15:22,270 --> 00:15:27,590
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

158
00:15:29,190 --> 00:15:34,350
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

159
00:15:35,790 --> 00:15:40,790
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

160
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:47,750
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

161
00:15:48,470 --> 00:15:55,110
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

162
00:15:55,550 --> 00:16:00,910
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

163
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:07,990
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

164
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:10,990
♪The promise we made♪

165
00:16:11,150 --> 00:16:14,630
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

166
00:16:14,830 --> 00:16:21,230
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

167
00:16:21,430 --> 00:16:27,510
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

168
00:16:28,230 --> 00:16:34,310
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

169
00:16:34,550 --> 00:16:39,350
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

170
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:42,830
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
